snippet: After three consecutive tournament exits against low-ranked opponents, Roger Federer pulled out of the Rogers Cup in Montreal, which starts Monday, without giving a reason.
abstract: Roger Federer pulls out of Rogers Cup event in Montreal, after three consecutive tournament exits against low-ranked opponents; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: After three consecutive tournament exits against low-ranked opponents, Roger Federer pulled out of the Rogers Cup in Montreal, which starts Monday, without giving a reason.
